@6
                              Ode Tae The Haggis
                 @5
                      Oh whit a sleekit horrible beastie
                     Lurks in yer belly efter the feastie
                      Just as ye sit doon among yer kin
                    There sterts to stir an enormous wind.

                     The neeps and tatties and mushy peas
                      Stert workin like a gentle breeze
                    But soon the puddin wi the sonsie face
                    Will hiv ye blawin all ower the place.

                       Nae matter whit the hell ye dae
                          A'bodys gonnae hiv tae pay
                          Even if ye try tae stifle
                        Its like a bullet oot a rifle.
@5
                       Hawd yer bum tight tae the chair
                         Tae try and stop leakin air
                       Shift yersel fae cheek tae cheek
                           Prae God it disnae reek.

                        But aw yer efforts go asunder
                      Oot it comes like a clap a thunder
                           Ricochets aroon the room
                           Michty me a sonic boom.

                         God almighty it fairly reeks
                         Hope I hivnae shit ma breeks
                         Tae the bog I better scurry
                      Aw whit the hell,it's no ma worry.
@5
                         A'body roon aboot me chokin
                           Wan or two nearly bokin
                         I'll feel better in a while
                        Cannae help but raise a smile.




                      Wis him! I shout wi accusin glower
                     Alas too late,he's jist keeled ower
                     Ye dirty bugger they shout and stare
                       A dinnae feel welcome any mair.

                    Where e're ye go let yer wind gan free
                       Sounds like jist the job fur me
                         Whit a fuss at Rabbies perty
                       Ower the sake o' wan wee farty!

]5@2
